# Project Architecture Complete — Gantt Chart Deployed

The React frontend has been successfully upgraded with native Enterprise visualization structures using `gantt-task-react` directly mapping to the Critical Path Engine built in the Backend!

## 1. Gantt Rendering 
- Successfully created `GanttView.tsx` matching exactly to the user dashboard requirements. 
- Integrated a live payload parsing the backend mapping to format strict SVG-based Gantt task blocks cleanly.
